    Tory~1nz (^American~3) an American who favored the British side during the American Revolution
    Tory~2nz (^right-winger~1) a supporter of traditional political and social institutions against the forces of reform
    Tory~3nz (^Englishman~1) a member of political party in Great Britain that has been known as the Conservative Party since 1832
